  m_text: 'You have been walking for hours, and there''s a storm approaching.


    Crash
    landed on an Alien planet you wonder if you will ever make it home again.


    You
    find a nearby abandoned building and go inside to wait out the storm.


    You
    explore the different rooms wondering what kind of life these winged aliens led.


    Eventualy
    you enter what looks like a workshop, you notice some strange mechanisms and
    diagrams on the table.


    A peculiar thought comes to mind...


    You wonder
    if you can put the machine back together.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
